Better Homes And Gardens Real Estate Main Street Properties

data.description: New lower price! Fantastic spacious floor-plan on this lovely 4 bedroom 2 and a half bath all brick home in Summerfield! As you walk in the door you will see a formal living room to the right, formal dining room to the left.  Straight ahead is the largest family room and kitchen you have ever seen! The chef’s kitchen has been updated with beautiful mosaic glass tile back splash, stainless appliances, quartz countertops, and so much cabinet and counter space!  A beautiful island is in the middle to help prep your meals.  There is a breakfast nook area as well.  The pantry and laundry room has a half bath.  The family room overlooks the large covered patio with ceiling fans.  The backyard is the perfect size for a pool.  There is a huge shed for your yard tools and more. As you walk past the family room you will see the primary suite on the left that has his and hers closets.  The primary bathroom has a double vanity, garden tub and a separate shower.  The other 3 bedrooms are nice sizes, and will accommodate all sizes of furniture.  Other features include hurricane storm panels, pre-wiring for surround sound and a Vivant Security system is paid for and will remain for new buyer.  Seller will install new architectural shingle roof with acceptable offer.  This quiet neighborhood is the perfect location close to I-10, get everywhere fast! Shopping, restaurants, and easy access to the beaches.  Don’t miss this beauty, book your showing today!
